ChKMVTh BNThH BYThH ChTShBH 'yMVDYH ShB'yH.
TBChH TBChH MSKH YYNH 'aPh 'yUrKH ShLChNH.
ShLChH N'yUrThYH ThQUr'a 'yL-GPhY MUrMY QUrTh.
MY-PhThY YSUr HNH ChSUr-LB 'aMUrH LV.
LKV LChMV BLChMY VShThV BYYN MSKThY.
'yZBV PhTh'aYM VChYV V'aShUrV BDUrK BYNH.
YSUr LTSh LQCh LV QLVN VMVKYCh LUrSh'y MVMV.
'aL-ThVKCh LTSh PhN-YShN'aK HVKCh LChKM VY'aHBK.
ThN LChKM VYChKM-'yVD HVD'y LTShDYQ VYVSPh LQCh.
ThChLTh ChKMH YUr'aTh YHVH VD'yTh QDShYM BYNH.
KY-BY YUrBV YMYK VYVSYPhV LK ShNVTh ChYYM.
'aM-ChKMTh ChKMTh LK VLTShTh LBDK ThSh'a.
'aShTh KSYLVTh HMYH PhThYVTh VBL-YD'yH MH.
VYShBH LPhThCh BYThH 'yL-KS'a MUrMY QUrTh.
LQUr'a L'yBUrY-DUrK HMYShUrYM 'aUrChVThM.
